---
title: Creamy Tomato Chicken Penne with Baby Spinach
description: A penne for your thoughts? Well, we’re thinking of tender chicken and pasta in a rich and creamy sauce. With baby spinach and courgette for goodness, and topped with Parmesan cheese, this is the bowl of your (and our) dreams!
